EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
UNTIED KINGDOM TO PORTUGAL.
31 FOOT S/V GOLDEN DAWN OF KENT, WHITE HULL, FOUR PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE LYMINGTON (50-75N 001-55W) TO PORTO (41-09N 008-37W).
VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO UKMRCC, PHONE: 4413 2631 7575,
